name: Vision IT Group
overview: VISION IT GROUP, founded in Belgium in 2001, led by Marc Urbany and Philippe Muffat-es-Jacques, is a European IT consulting and expertise group specialized in: IS management and performances optimization, software qualification, innovative business applications development, consulting and training. VISION IT GROUP has operations in 8 European countries (Belgium, France, Germany, Great Britain, Italy, Luxembourg, Spain, and Switzerland) and employs more than 1100 experts. Listed simultaneously on the Alternext NYSE-Euronext Brussels and Paris, VISION IT GROUP received the prize for best stock exchange performance in 2008 on the Alternext Brussels market.

acquisitions.source_description: VISION IT GROUP sets up in Germany with the acquisition of GFI Germany

milestones.description:
Vision IT Group continues its external growth strategy and sets up in the Netherlands.
Agreement finalization for the acquisition of Qwise, a consultancy firm specializing in virtualization of computer infrastructures.
